title: Personalized Princess
sinopse:
Bishie boy that got transfered and visited Ohn Noori, Lee Sun-Uh.
I was surely suprised that my father, who I never met myself, had sent him,
but to say he's one of my fiancée candidates!!!

AND WHAT?
My father is the king of a secret kingdom?
Oh my~ ♥
Then I...am a princess?

With two fiancée candidates, I ended up with a happy headache...
Ahhhh~♥
Who should I pick to make the right choice?

(Source: MangaFox)
